item.title: Who is Anthony Spezzano?
item.description: Anthony is currently completing the third year of his B.A., Spec. Hons. Cognitive Science. Anthony has a great passion for studying the brain, human behaviour and technology. Anthony's interests lie within many fields of discipline, but most recently it’s been the implementation of technology (or technological assistance/aid) into our daily life to help eliminate even the smallest of obstacles experienced by the average person, or the larger, more cumbersome hurdles, that affect so many.
